Package nefra.game

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Division
    Holds all the information required to make a division: name and match official fees.
    Game
    Game holds all the information necessary to "play" a game, it also works out the match fees payable to the referees and adds it both to the clubs and to the referees fees.
    GUIFunctions
    The functions for the Game and Division GUIs (Create, Edit, View)
